      <h3>Plumbers & HVAC</h3>
      <p>Higher LTV ($2,500 for recurring maintenance relationships) but also higher Google Ads CPC ($25/click). This means SEO ROI is especially strong. Equivalent ad spend would be $625/month for the same 25 organic clicks. Emergency service keywords convert at 12%+.</p>

